Students are enemies, defeat/educate them with your towers! If they reach the end, you lose lives.
Press BLACK (while in-game) to enter the buy menu, and PINK to select! Move the towers around with the joystick, and PINK again to place!
Remember, different towers have different abilities, which you can check out in the buy menu. Press BLUE to speed the game up!

Teacher TD is a tower defense game where you can play with the American School of the Hague teachers, to educate students. 
(Move to the joystick to go forward/back)
